{"tid":949841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"敏感肌用咩洗面同護膚好？","createTime":"2018-12-21T05:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T06:19:13.000Z","uid":113657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e1905df00444d73b60b2b4776301505f5f9da0f9","tid":949841,"uid":113657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:43:57.000Z","msg":"早前用b5 gel好似敏感咁樣  又好易塊面紅左一撻撻咁  <br />\n有冇咩牌子推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1225bb771e4560b46d1e4fe3568d58000d9723e6","tid":949841,"uid":113657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"上網睇又唔識分邊d係打手   定係我應該去睇一睇皮膚科先？"},{"pid":"98aea2d6f25eeb771d5754c3205af7a339aa96c8","tid":949841,"uid":113657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e0233d4303cee86271948442a1fb89290cac1f","tid":949841,"uid":13752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"你有無試過用過某啲護膚品真係敏感<br />\n紅腫/痛/生左好多粒粒好痕etc.<br />\n有嘅話 你睇下中招個幾件產品嘅成份表<br />\n將共通嘅成份抽出黎 上cosdna 個網查下呢幾個成份邊個會引起不良反應<br />\n<br />\n我之前敷過幾隻面膜第2日爛面 紅腫又刺熱又痕<br />\n原來自己對某隻防腐劑敏感<br />\n之後買咩護膚品都睇住成份表 就無再中過伏<br />\n<br />\n我本身都容易泛紅/敏感 同埋我混合性皮膚<br />\n買啲for敏感肌用嘅會好啲<br />\n最好唔好有香料 同埋太多防腐劑<br />\nAvene/Curel 呢兩款我用過都ok<br />\nAvene 個隻乜鳩保濕噴霧唔好買<br />\n化妝水/保濕精華/cream mask/乳液都ok<br />\nCurel 化妝水ok 但啲乳液/乳霜對我太潤..."},{"pid":"9b3fcf69074732f10c7acf5790440b7c399ecb83","tid":949841,"uid":113657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:01:28.000Z","msg":"謝回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我嗰種係用手掂一掂塊面就紅嗰種   所以洗完面  搽乜都好似會敏感咁樣   好腫又未試過  痕痕哋有紅點就成日"},{"pid":"c7509635db1a59d768636f5ba9875a261a4a5118","tid":949841,"uid":106149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:02:06.000Z","msg":"應該用精液最好<br />\n之前用精液洗臉  皮膚好過雞蛋"},{"pid":"37be964a717aa0d21eb00fc94e4dd7376f0bf2ee","tid":949841,"uid":113657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:02:56.000Z","msg":"基本除左洗面  其實應該搽乜好呢"},{"pid":"226ce7aff662494e23c4745006cfd6be016bbd19","tid":949841,"uid":194687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:05:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc97c2fa9679647e9e42feb74b671d228e2665f5","tid":949841,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7509635db1a59d768636f5ba9875a261a4a5118","tid":949841,"uid":106149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:02:06.000Z","msg":"應該用精液最好<br />\n之前用精液洗臉  皮膚好過雞蛋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"我可以比啲你<br />\n要唔要"}]}